Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So for this problem—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:09.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi, why did you decide to go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko-chan, you're calling me Ma-kun,\Nnot Akagi. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.51,sign_1662_5_Authority,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,550)}Authority
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:16.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are we seriously doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:19.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not answering your question\Nunless you call me Ma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Say it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:27.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:30.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, we were talking\Nabout something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I was going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What did you even see in me anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, we were in the middle\Nof something serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I was going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do I like about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your face, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:49.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So my personality doesn't matter, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:54.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You have a cute face, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care about\Nwhat's on the inside at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Again, not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute, Ryoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then what if you found someone cuter than me?\NWould you go for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:11.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:13.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got plenty of things going for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:14.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like your boobs—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Face, boobs... That's all you care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:19.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care about who I am, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think I do care about what's on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's so good about me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:29.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:32.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're short-tempered and crass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}sorry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a pain in the ass\Nwhen you sulk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we break up already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you've got a lot of problems, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I still like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You just like my boobs or some shit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I like your personality, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your short temper, your crassness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obsessed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:09.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you're happy, you can show it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute,\Nyou make me want to bully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me you like me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want me to tell you I {\i1}love{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, tell me you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Tell me, {\i1}please{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Ma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.69,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Things got good with my boyfriend\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.15,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But we ended up not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even dramas get special effects these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.74,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us has been able\Nto make a move since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.50,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've been avoiding that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.67,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:57.84,sign_5586_76_X_File,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,550)}X-File
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I wonder if he's embarrassed\Nthat he got cockblocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.52,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't bother me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind him\Nbeing a bit more aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:05.93,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I'd feel weird\Nabout bringing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So have you seen it, Kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:07.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What were we talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We said we'd get our comedy ideas from dramas\Nbecause "bang" was getting old, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So let's try me as the detective\Nand you as the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I've never seen that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:30.28,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't care about\Ncomedy ideas right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,FBI! Hands behind your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:35.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:37.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! You've let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,D-Despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You too, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we've broken character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.86,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did he try to kiss me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.36,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.42,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's gonna do it via skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.36,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, you can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll be an alien next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.45,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the FBI agent this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, all right, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A-Assuming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.89,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming he was trying to kiss me,\Nthis set up can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.26,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! Are you for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.77,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Er... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This bit doesn't have a punch line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We need to come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:58.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.08,sign_8596_123_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:04.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you like movies,\Nso if you're up for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you tomorrow at the theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.57,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.69,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,How did the exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:20.52,sign_8982_128_We_Don_t_Need_Gi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,550)}We Don't Need Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:20.24,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, you were\Nthinking about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.28,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,We have plans to see\Na movie tomorrow, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:29.31,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so excited about it,\NI couldn't focus on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was that tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.32,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.87,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to watch Magic Shin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.72,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I never miss a movie in that series.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can we do that the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I actually have—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:48.55,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,It better not be a jezebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.54,sign_9722_143_Jezebel,,0000,0000,0000,,Jezebel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.44,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.02,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,You? With a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:07:01.90,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Such vile pigs deserve not to bask\Nin the youth of we whom they deem gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I hate girls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was invited by a guy friend, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.73,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have friends besides me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,M-My friend from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He texted that we should catch up—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:16.08,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.79,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Then I, Motoyama Tomomichi, shall yield\Nto your previous engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.11,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,We are nothing if not repulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.66,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the bonds of our friendships\Nare our greatest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.71,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Do kindly introduce me\Nto your friend someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.94,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I shall watch the movie by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.62,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good man, Motoyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.22,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.22,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I lie just to spend time with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.23,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you tomorrow at the theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.73,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worthless. I don't need a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.25,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Motoyama-kun, I'm lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have another friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My phonebook is only your number\Nand my parents', and in fact—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.57,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.74,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, confiding in me a shameful truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.83,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I have never had the pleasure \Nof having a soulmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.58,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you must do tomorrow, Yamane-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:08.67,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I shall not pry further,\Nif you are inclined to hide it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it's just that a girl I know\Nasked me to watch a movie with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We actually had lunch together before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but we didn't really hit it off, so I don't\Nknow why she's inviting me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:33.78,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}lied{\i0} to keep a {\i1}woman{\i0} hidden from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Motoyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go with you tomorrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.99,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I implore you to choose her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.28,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,It warrants no mention\Nthat I despise women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.90,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I would like nothing more\Nthan to render blind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.63,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,those eyes with which they gaze upon me\Nas though I am foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.03,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.85,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Just how could I possibly find fault\Nin so pure a maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.26,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,that she would call upon\Nas repugnant a man as Yamane-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.64,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.21,sign_12915_194_I_am_overjoyed__,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I am overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.42,sign_12915_194_I_am_overjoyed__,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.16,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Have the two of you\Nentered into a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:08.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're really just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even that's presumptuous of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know\Nwhat she's thinking, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.62,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that is a platonic relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's going to bring her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind hanging out with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.26,Default,Third Wheel,0000,0000,0000,,Any friend of yours\Nis perfectly acceptable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.13,sign_8596_123_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.71,Italics,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people come to me for dating advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.68,Italics,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never been in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.56,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Why do people ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.12,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.42,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.32,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:50.37,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't care\Nto talk to girls from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.36,Italics,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.86,Italics,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Why was he in the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.99,sign_14242_217_Dating_Master,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,550)}Dating Master
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.79,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come out, little kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.32,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Were you helping a kitten stuck in the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.95,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I just felt like climbing the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.60,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.25,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.13,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.04,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,You just had the same troubled look\Non your face as that kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.61,Italics,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this guy,\Ncalling me a cute little kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.80,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think I'm a dating master, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.31,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.27,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.98,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.56,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Dating master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.53,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're cool or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.61,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:40.32,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing cool about a man\Nwho's made more girls cry than smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.76,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, I'd better stop\Ncalling myself the dating master,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.46,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,or the dating gods will smite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.20,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.33,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.68,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.92,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.76,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.26,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.51,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.59,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oui{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.34,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.87,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, my kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.02,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}everyone's{\i0} prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.64,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Fall for me, and you'll get burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.00,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.53,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,That's just my afterimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.27,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, my kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.24,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,No one can hold me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.37,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:30.58,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, help me like you helped that kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.37,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.69,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.29,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Silly kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:43.01,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.53,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:51.52,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.20,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,It's the spaghetti I had for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.19,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.02,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I was being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.75,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Being stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.03,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:04.38,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a prince's job to save\Na kitten in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.03,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.73,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.73,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put yourself in danger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.32,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.04,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.44,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Katori Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.75,Default,Senpai,0000,0000,0000,,Toodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:23.83,Default,Nagoya Curls,0000,0000,0000,,Katori-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.04,Italics,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: It's All the Fever's Fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.92,Next_Ep,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}It's All the Fever's Fault
